Outlier Calculation

In[143]:
import numpy as np
q1 = np.quantile(release_data, 0.25)
q2 = np.quantile(release_data, 0.50)
q3 = np.quantile(release_data, 0.75)

iqr=q3-q1

lb=q1-1.5*iqr
ub=q3+1.5*iqr

o_con1=release_data<lb
o_con2=release_data>ub
o_df=churn_df[o_con1|o_con2]

w_o_con1 = release_data>lb
w_o_con2 = release_data<ub
w_outlier_df=churn_df[w_o_con1&w_o_con2]

plt.figure(figsize=(14,3))
